Currently, Asia Pacific holds the largest market share in the conveyor belt fasteners market, followed by North America and Europe.

5. What are the most commonly used types of conveyor belt fasteners?
The most commonly used types of conveyor belt fasteners include steel belt lacings, hinged belt fasteners, and bolt solid plate fasteners.

